divs: Sighting DetailsWell,my wife and I just watch a ufo pass over our home in Brampton.It was only a couple of thousand feet up no sound and one solid bright white light moving from north -west to south-east towards Dixie and Queen.maybe 10 secounts after the ufo cross over our home a jet at a much higher altitude crossed over it's path and you could see the plane's light's very clearly. The sighting was at 9:45pm partly cloudy skys
